  "observations": [
    "Match percentage ('Подходит вам на 82%') embedded directly in vacancy card — derived signal reducing scroll cognitive load",
    "Salary range visually emphasized with bold typography as primary scanning anchor",
    "Verification badges ('Открытый работодатель', 'Готов к удалёнке') as trust signals on card",
    "Quick-apply: one-tap 'Откликнуться' with optional modal for resume selection + cover letter",
    "Applications funnel visualized as timeline of recruiter actions inside card (Sent → Viewed → Invited/Rejected)",
    "Status-segmented tabs in Applications section: All / Invitations / Rejections / Archived",
    "Push notifications tied to application.status transitions",
    "Integrated messenger scoped to application context — vacancy header persistently pinned at top of chat",
    "Pre-built message templates as quick-action buttons for common recruiter responses",
    "Resume creation as 6-step wizard with inline contextual tooltips per field",
    "Multiple resumes per user — each targeted at different job types",
    "Filter chips as primary UX with escape hatch to heavyweight advanced-search sheet (15+ params)",
    "Monetization surfaces (Premium, resume boost) rendered as banners in main feed and applications — commercially aggressive",
    "Bottom tab bar with 5 sections as top-level navigation spine"
  ]
}